      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775404297283,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For a small shop design a system through which the shop owner can\n\n1. Add a new product\n2. update/delete existing prodcut\n3. list all the product on thr website\n4. customer should be able to quickly access the catalog\n5. Payment is out of the scope for the problem statement",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For a small shop design a system through which the shop owner can\n\n1. Add a new product\n2. update/delete existing prodcut\n3. list all the product on thr website\n4. customer should be able to quickly access the catalog\n5. Payment is out of the scope for the problem statement",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
